    prompt: "A patient in the ICU has a heart rate of 120 bpm and a known history of dilated cardiomyopathy. On auscultation, you hear a single prominent extra heart sound in diastole rather than two distinct extra sounds. Which of the following best predicts when this merged sound will DISAPPEAR?",
